My D&amp;D experience is limited to a game I got in about 11 years ago.  The DM at the time ended up getting super busy with classes and one of the 4 PCs ended up quitting the first day due to girl friend issues so the group fell apart quickly.<br />
<br />
(Oh and D&amp;D Online which doesn't really count)<br />
<br />
<br />
Altho some friends are currently starting a play by email campaign.  I'm gonna be a tiefling rogue, weeee!</div>
